<section id="how-it-works" class="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-tag">Simple Setup</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">One-Click <span class="gradient-text">Freedom</span></h2>
      <p class="section-desc">From download to uncensored internet in under 60 seconds.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">01</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Download & Run</h3>
          <p>Grab the latest release, extract the archive, and run <code>unbound.exe</code> as Administrator. All dependencies (WinDivert, Lua scripts, winws2 engine) are embedded — nothing else to install.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">02</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Hit Auto-Tune</h3>
          <p>Click "Автоподбор" (Auto-Tune). Unbound parallel-tests 70+ bypass profiles against YouTube, Discord, Telegram, Instagram, Twitter, and RuTracker. Smart scoring finds the profile that unblocks everything.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">03</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Connect & Forget</h3>
          <p>Press "ПОДКЛЮЧИТЬ!" and browse freely. Enable silent auto-start in settings — Unbound launches minimized to system tray on boot. Set it and forget it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-note">
      <h4>Under the Hood</h4>
      <p>Unbound uses the <strong>zapret2</strong> (winws2) engine by bol-van, which manipulates TCP packets at the DPI level using techniques like <strong>TCP desynchronization</strong> and <strong>packet reordering (Multidisorder)</strong>. Unlike VPNs, your traffic never leaves your direct connection — only blocked domains get modified packets.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.how-it-works {
  padding: 8rem 2rem;
  position: relative;
}

.container {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.section-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 4rem;
}

